<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7571> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7571" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Tr. pl. and legatus. In MRR 2.468 and 482 spell his name as Coelius. See Syme, JRS 53, 1963, 55RP 2.557-558; Wiseman, NM 225, no. 128; Shackleton Bailey, Studies 28, and Onom. Latiniensis may mean \"of the Ager Latiniensis.\"\n" .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/6774> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #6774" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/3> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Cic. Leg. Man. 58; cf. CIL 1(2).2.1441. Before 66. See Tribunes of the Plebs of uncertain date." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/6625> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #6625" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/3> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "One of a group named by Cicero as examples of persons who held the tribunate in one year and became Legates in the next (Cic. Leg. Man. 58, 66 B. C.). See CIL 1(2).2.1441." .
